11:55.515 --> 11:56.716
[ Laughs ]

11:56.716 --> 11:58.051
Oh, wait.
Huh?

11:58.051 --> 11:59.919
Is this that cart?
The guy?

11:59.919 --> 12:03.089
Remember, we got tacos here
and then we went home and we...

12:04.190 --> 12:05.425
What are you
talking about?

12:05.425 --> 12:08.094
