No, no.

13:41.888 --> 13:43.623
Martin, no!

13:43.623 --> 13:45.024
Martin, no!

13:45.024 --> 13:46.259
Hey! Stop it!

13:46.259 --> 13:48.594
Hey, hey, hey!
No, no, no, no, no, no!

13:49.629 --> 13:51.230
Ohhhh!

13:55.234 --> 13:56.502
Martin: So, let me
get this straight --

13:56.502 --> 13:57.770
