gonna kill me.

14:13.986 --> 14:15.154
It sounds more like a lie

14:15.154 --> 14:16.823
than the actual lies
I've told her.

14:25.565 --> 14:26.966
Oh, good news --
your sister

14:26.966 --> 14:29.302
and the guy she's been dating
are gonna grab us.

14:30.737 --> 14:32.772
What guy
she's been dating?

14:39.812 --> 14:41.681
I'm confused.

14:41.681 --> 14:42.882
So am I.

14:42.882 --> 14:44.484
When did
this happen?

14:44.484 --> 14:46.552
It didn't.
Oh, cut it out, Gene.

14:46.552 --> 14:48.955
He's reluctant
but present.

14:48.955 --> 14:50.189
Like Dad.

14:50.189 --> 14:51.624
I thought
your relationship with Gene

14:51.624 --> 14:53.526
was primarily bread-based,

14:53.526 --> 14:55.194
in that
he brings you bread.

14:55.194 --> 14:56.763
But not just bread.

14:56.763 --> 14:58.598
He also got me
these potato skins.

14:58.598 --> 14:59.799
I got those for me.

14:59.799 --> 15:00.800
[ Chuckles ]

15:00.800 --> 15:02.769
[ Singsong voice ]
Incoming PDA!

15:03.770 --> 15:06.372
