you know?

15:06.372 --> 15:08.407
He's mean.
"Gene."

15:08.407 --> 15:10.176
Look, I've been very clear
with your sister,

15:10.176 --> 15:11.844
but she's like
a dog with a bone.

15:11.844 --> 15:12.845
A dog!

15:12.845 --> 15:14.313
With a bone!

15:14.313 --> 15:15.815
And when is a dog
happier?

15:15.815 --> 15:18.284
Don't finish all
the potato skins. I want some.

15:18.284 --> 15:20.887
