like a potato skin.

15:26.726 --> 15:32.398
♪♪

15:32.398 --> 15:34.634
Steady.
Two step--

15:37.036 --> 15:38.871
What happened to you?

15:38.871 --> 15:40.339
None taken.

15:40.339 --> 15:42.308
Wait. Did you say
"No offense"?

15:42.308 --> 15:43.409
No.

15:43.409 --> 15:45.545
I like
sloppy and toasted Lena.

15:45.545 --> 15:46.913
She's like if Lena
lived in a trailer

15:46.913 --> 15:49.148
and started laundering money
in the Ozarks.

15:49.148 --> 15:50.616
I just binged "Ozark."

15:50.616 --> 15:52.018
I love Laura Linney.

15:52.018 --> 15:53.352
Okay, look.

15:53.352 --> 15:54.687
This is our first
parent/teacher night,

15:54.687 --> 15:56.189
and we're trying to make
a good first impression.

15:56.189 --> 15:58.224
Since we're not real parents,
there's strike one.

15:58.224 --> 16:02.762
But this -- this could easily
be strikes two and three,

16:02.762 --> 16:04.030
so bye.

16:04.030 --> 16:05.364
Arthur: Bye!

16:05.364 --> 16:06.966
[ Indistinct conversations ]

16:06.966 --> 16:09.202
Dodson. Hey,
nice to see you again.

16:09.202 --> 16:10.136
Hi.

16:10.136 --> 16:11.070
Dig the tie.

16:11.070 --> 16:12.438
Oh! Shakespeare.

16:12.438 --> 16:13.806
Duh. I know that.

16:15.174 --> 16:16.976
Lena. Hello.
Hey.

16:16.976 --> 16:20.146
I've been preparing all semester
for your visit.

16:20.146 --> 16:23.482
Here is a written defense
of my lesson plan,

16:23.482 --> 16:25.952
a schedule
of my after-school availability.

16:25.952 --> 16:27.320
I'm sorry about Thursdays.

16:27.320 --> 16:29.088
I have physical therapy
for a torn meniscus.

16:29.088 --> 16:31.924
