just in case you lost the copy

16:39.398 --> 16:41.434
that you subpoenaed
last year.

16:43.302 --> 16:45.137
[ Papers slap ]

16:45.137 --> 16:46.973
Life's too short, man.

16:46.973 --> 16:50.142
Seriously, I'm just stoked that
you're dedicating your life

16:50.142 --> 16:51.944
to helping the children,

16:51.944 --> 16:55.214
A.K.A., our future.

16:55.214 --> 16:56.415
Is she on something?

16:56.415 --> 16:58.050
She is, yeah.
[ Chuckling ] Oh.

16:58.050 --> 16:59.619
Can it be permanent?

16:59.619 --> 17:02.588
Listen, baby, you're doing
the best you can,

17:02.588 --> 17:04.357
and that's all
one can ask for

17:04.357 --> 17:06.959
in this crazy,
mixed-up world.

17:06.959 --> 17:07.994
I love you.

17:09.228 --> 17:11.998
I love you so much.

17:13.266 --> 17:14.233
Okay.

17:14.233 --> 17:15.868
Okay, let's boogie.

17:15.868 --> 17:18.004
Uh, yeah, we have
some other teachers to meet.

17:18.004 --> 17:19.372
[ Cellphone buzzing ]

17:19.372 --> 17:21.240
[ Groans, clears throat ]

17:21.240 --> 17:23.142
If you need to go have sex
with your girlfriend --
