to be my caretaker.

17:26.279 --> 17:27.413
Yes, you do.

17:27.413 --> 17:29.315
The universe
will look after me.

17:29.315 --> 17:30.516
No, it won't.

17:30.516 --> 17:32.118
[ Buzzing continues ]

17:32.118 --> 17:33.552
Well, let's see.

17:33.552 --> 17:35.454
I can take the call
and tell her that, once again,

17:35.454 --> 17:38.958
I am blowing off our plans
to spend time with you

17:38.958 --> 17:40.893
or I can let it
go to voicemail

17:40.893 --> 17:43.429
and accept
that it's pretty much over.

17:43.429 --> 17:45.331
[ Buzzing continues ]

17:45.331 --> 17:47.934
[ Buzzing stops ]

17:47.934 --> 17:51.170
Well, you know what they say --
"No woman, no cry."

17:51.938 --> 17:55.141
Yeah, that's actually
not the meaning of that song.

17:55.141 --> 17:59.245
And if you're gonna make the
rounds as a white Rasta lady,

17:59.245 --> 18:01.414
